'''Túro''' is an enigmatic character, apparently old ("''[[Yára]] Túro''"). Although the lore surrounding him deals with [[Quenya/Grammar|Quenya grammar]], it is unknown if he belongs to the [[legendarium]]. Some people were interested in him, due to his coming and making unspecified things, and he ended up annoying them by eating all of the bread.<ref>{{PE|22c}}, pp. 118-9</ref>

